<h3 id="alcohol">Alcohol</h3>

<p>This section summarises information on drinking behaviours, alcohol specific hospital admissions, and alcohol specific mortality.</p>

<p><a href="/ccgs/coastal/wider-determinants/alcohol/">Read more on Alcohol</a></p>

<h3 id="tobacco">Tobacco</h3>

<p>This section presents data on smoking prevalence amongst different age groups, smoking during pregnancy, and smoking attributable to mortality.</p>

<p><a href="/ccgs/coastal/wider-determinants/tobacco/">Read more on Tobacco</a></p>

<h3 id="physical-activity">Physical Activity</h3>

<p>This section summarises the guidance and data available on physical activity.</p>

<p><a href="/ccgs/coastal/wider-determinants/physical-activity/">Read more on Physical Activity</a></p>

<h3 id="weight-and-healthy-eating">Weight and Healthy Eating</h3>

<p>This section summarises the data collected as part of the National Child Measurement Programme (NCMP) on the weight of children in reception and year 6. This section also provides estimates of adult obesity and healthy eating.</p>

<p><a href="/ccgs/coastal/wider-determinants/weight-and-healthy-eating/">Read more on Weight and Healthy Eating</a></p>

<h3 id="mental-health">Mental Health</h3>

<p>This section collates information on mental health such as the estimated prevalence of specific mental health problems, including depression, psychosis and suicide.</p>

<p><a href="/ccgs/coastal/wider-determinants/mental-health/">Read more on Mental Health</a></p>
